Package java.lang.classfile.instructionPREVIEW

Interface NopInstruction

All Superinterfaces:
ClassFileElementPREVIEW, CodeElementPREVIEW, InstructionPREVIEW
public sealed interface NopInstruction extends InstructionPREVIEW
NopInstruction is a preview API of the Java platform.
Programs can only use NopInstruction when preview features are enabled.
Preview features may be removed in a future release, or upgraded to permanent features of the Java platform.
Models a nop invocation instruction in the code array of a Code attribute. Delivered as a CodeElementPREVIEW when traversing the elements of a CodeModelPREVIEW.
